headline: 2 Reasons to Like TRV (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: While the S&P 500 is up 15.6% since March 2025, Travelers (currently trading at $277 per share) has lagged behind, posting a return of 6.8%. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
